Title: Worcester Bosch Greenstar Ri Compact ErP 27Ri LPG ErP regular LPG boiler
Description: A compact, wall-mounted boiler ideal for small and medium homes, the Worcester Bosch Greenstar 27Ri ErP LPG regular boiler is straightforward to install and user-friendly, controlled by a intuitive display and simple knob system. Featuring a groundbreaking new heat exchanger, this ErP A-rated boiler promises greater than ever efficiency, improved reliability and enhanced durability. The Greenstar is compatible with a wide range of controls as well as Greenskies solar panels and high efficiency Greenstore water cylinders, giving homeowners the option to build the system that best suits their needs.
